<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Denied</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0f1115;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #1a1d24;
            border: 1px solid #2e333d;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #ef4444;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .description {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .dropdown-btn {
            background-color: #2e333d;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .dropdown-btn:hover {
            background-color: #3f4654;
        }

        .dropdown-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        .dropdown-btn .arrow {
            transition: transform 0.2s;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .dropdown-btn.active .arrow {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
        }

        .dropdown-content {
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out, margin-top 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
            background-color: #14161d;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .dropdown-content.show {
            max-height: 300px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #2e333d;
        }

        .dropdown-content ol {
            padding: 20px 25px;
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        .dropdown-content li {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .dropdown-content li:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="icon">🚫</div>
        <h1>You have your IP blocked.</h1>
        <p class="description">
            Your IP has been blocked. Meaning anything that has Peer to Peer connection will automatically block you {if can} or make me leave the lobby.
        </p>

        <button class="dropdown-btn" onclick="toggleDropdown()">
            What does this mean? <span class="arrow">▼</span>
        </button>

        <div class="dropdown-content" id="dropdownMenu">
            <ol>
                <li>1. Means you can not Communicate with me.</li>
                <li>2. Your IP has been Blocked Meaning no interaction AT all.</li>
                <li>3. Yes it is not hard to get an IP you can basically use Wireshark with anything Peer to Peer.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleDropdown() {
            const button = document.querySelector('.dropdown-btn');
            const content = document.getElementById('dropdownMenu');
            
            button.classList.toggle('active');
            content.classList.toggle('show');
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
